  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA56">
<l>vaṭuvaṉ ṟeṉakkaruti nīmatitti yāyiṉ</l>
<l>cuṭuveṇ poṭiniṟattāy collāy - paṭuveṇ</l>
<l>pulāṟṟalaiyi ṉuḷḷuṇ puṟampēcak kēṭṭō</l>
<l>nilāttalaiyiṟ cūṭuvāy nī</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If you consider and think it is not a stain,</l>
<l>you with the colour of the hot white ash, speak, since [I] have heard</l>
<l>speaking behind [your] back of the food from a fallen, white, meet-reeking skull,</l>
<l>o you who wear the moonlight on [your] head.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
